gust 29, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: Some people among the bedouins would bring us meat and we did not know if the name of Allah was mentioned over it or not. The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cMention the name of Allah over it and eat.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5680,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/29\/animal-targets-haram\/","url_meta":{"origin":6174,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Carrion: Unlawful to eat an animal used for target practice","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 29, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Tha\u2019labah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAn animal used as a target is not lawful.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 4438 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani Al-Sindi said, \"The meaning is that it becomes carrion, which is not lawful to eat, and using it as\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28106,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/23\/allah-has-waived-fasting-half-of-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":6174,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Travel: Allah has waived fasting, half of prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 23, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Amr ibn Umayyah reported: I came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, from a journey and he said, \u201cStay to eat, O Abu Umayyah.\u201d I said, \u201cIndeed, I am fasting.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cCome close to me and I will tell you about the traveler.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34037,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/03\/03\/prophet-washes-hands\/","url_meta":{"origin":6174,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Hygiene: The Prophet washes his hands before eating","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 3, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, if he wanted to sleep while he was in a state of major ritual impurity, he would perform ablution. If he wanted to eat or drink, he would first wash his hands and then eat or drink. Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14887,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/10\/must-eat-suhoor\/","url_meta":{"origin":6174,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Suhur: Eat the blessed pre-fasting meal","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 10, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Miqdam ibn Ma\u2019dikarib reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYou must take the pre-fasting meal, for it is a blessed meal.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 2164 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0642\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0627\u06